data.description: Looking for lots of space?? You've found it! This beautiful 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, 2 car garage home is ready for new owners! This home offers a light and bright foyer that opens to the large living area and spacious kitchen. The kitchen has plenty of cabinet space, granite counters, and large pantry. Downstairs also has a formal dining room, bonus space, and sun room. Upstairs has 5 bedrooms a shared bathroom and the laundry room. The primary suite has 2 closets, dual vanity, soaker tub, and separate shower. The living area is situated at the back of the home and opens to a large deck that is perfect for entertaining! Come see!
